Sexy older woman teases internet with saucy video of her doing THIS with fruit Sexy older woman teases internet with saucy video of her doing THIS with fruit AN ATTRACTIVE 50-year-old woman has sent the internet wild again in a new video where she playfully poses with fruit. / Published 20th March 2017 
Jennifer King, 50, went viral twice last week for sharing clips of her trying on a tight T-shirt with no bra and stripping naked before walking outdoors. 
And now she's got viewers hot under the collar again. 
In the above video Jennifer hangs around the house in a revealing bikini as she shows fans that it's snowing in her home town of North Carolina, US. 
The brunette then gives viewers a quick tutorial focusing on how to boil the perfect pot of coffee. 
But after taking viewers on a tour of their home and showing off a few household appliances, things get inexplicably saucy. 
YOUTUBE/BANSHEEMOON FRUITY: Jennifer King holds melons and pineapples in front of her boobs in the above video “Look at these nice melons” Jennifer King 
Jennifer suddenly strips off her top and holds a pair of melons in front of her chest and says to the camera: "Look at these nice melons." 
The clip then cuts to her holding a pair of pineapples in front of her boobs before grabbing two sweetcorn ears and doing the same again. 
Her husband laughs and says: "Now you're just being corny." 
With no explanation as to why she stripped off, Jennifer then puts her clothes back on and ventures out into the snow with her pet dog.
